<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="lo">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="ລາຍລະອຽດລົດມືສອງ <%- car.brand %> <%- car.model %> <%- car.year %>">
    <title>ລາຍລະອຽດລົດ</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+Lao:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-dark">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">
                <img src="/images/logo.png" alt="Logo" style="height: 80px; margin-right: 15px;">
                ລົດມືສອງຄຸນນະພາບ
            </a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav" aria-controls="navbarNav" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
                <div class="navbar-nav ms-auto">
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/">ໜ້າຫຼັກ</a>
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/sell-car">ສະເໜີຂາຍລົດ</a>
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/contact">ຕິດຕໍ່</a>
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/admin/login">ແອດມິນ</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="container mt-4">
        <div class="card bg-dark text-light">
            <div class="card-header bg-gold text-dark">
                <h2><%- car.brand %> <%- car.model %> <%- car.year %></h2>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <% if (car.images && car.images.length > 0) { %>
                            <div id="carImageCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel">
                                <div class="carousel-inner">
                                    <% car.images.forEach((image, index) => { %>
                                        <div class="carousel-item <%= index === 0 ? 'active' : '' %>">
                                            <img src="<%- image %>" class="d-block w-100" alt="Car Image">
                                        </div>
                                    <% }) %>
                                </div>
                                <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#carImageCarousel" data-bs-slide="prev">
                                    <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                                    <span class="visually-hidden">ກ່ອນໜ້າ</span>
                                </button>
                                <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#carImageCarousel" data-bs-slide="next">
                                    <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                                    <span class="visually-hidden">ຕໍ່ໄປ</span>
                                </button>
                            </div>
                        <% } else { %>
                            <img src="/images/placeholder.jpg" class="img-fluid" alt="Placeholder">
                        <% } %>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <h3>ລາຍລະອຽດລົດ</h3>
                        <p><strong>ລາຄາ:</strong> <%- car.price.toLocaleString() %> ກີບ</p>
                        <p><strong>ແຂວງ:</strong> <%- car.province %></p>
                        <p><strong>ເກຍ:</strong> <%- car.transmission === 'Automatic' ? 'ອັດຕະໂນມັດ' : 'ຄູ່ມື' %></p>
                        <% if (car.mileage) { %>
                            <p><strong>ໄມລ໌:</strong> <%- car.mileage.toLocaleString() %> ກິໂລແມັດ</p>
                        <% } %>
                        <p><strong>ລາຍລະອຽດ:</strong> <%- car.description || 'ບໍ່ມີລາຍລະອຽດ' %></p>
                        <p><strong>ຜູ້ຂາຍ:</strong> <%- car.sellerName %> (<%- car.sellerPhone %>)</p>
                        <div class="quality-badges">
                            <% if (car.inspected && car.inspected.noFlood) { %>
                                <span class="badge bg-success">ບໍ່ເຄີຍຖືກນໍ້າຖ້ວມ</span>
                            <% } %>
                            <% if (car.inspected && car.inspected.noMajorAccident) { %>
                                <span class="badge bg-success">ບໍ່ເຄີຍປະສົບອຸປະຕິເຫດໜັກ</span>
                            <% } %>
                            <% if (car.inspected && car.inspected.noFire) { %>
                                <span class="badge bg-success">ບໍ່ເຄີຍໄຟໄໝ້</span>
                            <% } %>
                            <% if (car.isPremium) { %>
                                <span class="badge bg-gold text-dark">ພຣີມຽມ</span>
                            <% } %>
                        </div>
                        <a href="tel:<%- car.sellerPhone %>" class="btn btn-gold mt-3">ໂທຫາຜູ້ຂາຍ</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="footer text-center bg-dark text-gold">
        <div class="container">
            <p>ທີ່ຢູ່: ນະຄອນຫຼວງວຽງຈັນ, ປະເທດລາວ</p>
            <p>ໂທ: +856 20 1234 5678</p>
            <p>ອີເມວ: contact@yourcarwebsite.com</p>
            <p>ຕິດຕາມພວກເຮົາ:
                <a href="https://www.facebook.com/yourpage" target="_blank" class="text-gold mx-2">Facebook</a> |
                <a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@your.tiktok" target="_blank" class="text-gold mx-2">TikTok</a>
            </p>
            <p>ດາວໂຫຼດແອັບ:
                <a href="https://play.google.com/store" target="_blank" class="text-gold mx-2">Google Play</a> |
                <a href="https://www.apple.com/app-store/" target="_blank" class="text-gold mx-2">App Store</a>
            </p>
            <p>© 2025 Used Car Sales. ສະຫງວນລິຂະສິດ.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>